      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Please do not mix your diazepam with alcohol, even a small glass of wine. Combining these substances can dangerously enhance the sedative effects of the medication, increasing the risk of extreme drowsiness, slowed breathing, and impaired judgment. For safe and effective sleep, please stick to taking your prescribed diazepam exactly as your doctor directed. If you have concerns about its effectiveness or sleep patterns, talk to your healthcare provider first.",
